# Frontend JSX Conventions

```javascript
// API base — always use this
import { API_BASE } from "@/lib/api";

// Fetch pattern
const res = await fetch(`${API_BASE}/contact/`, {
  method: "POST",
  headers: { "Content-Type": "application/json", "Accept": "application/json" },
  body: JSON.stringify(payload),
});

// Styling — Tailwind + cn() helper
import { cn } from "@/lib/utils";
```

- Functional components only
- Local `useState` for form/fetch state (Redux is scaffolded but unused)
- New pages: add to `routes.js` + `App.jsx` + `navmenu.jsx`
- Document in `.cursor/workflow/pages-and-routes.md`
